        <updateDate>2021-06-29T13:47:30Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong></strong>This bill requires the&nbsp;Department of Transportation and the Department&nbsp;of Energy&nbsp;to jointly establish a working group to make recommendations on the development, adoption, and integration of certain electric vehicles into&nbsp;U.S. transportation and energy systems. In addition, the working group must develop, electronically publish, and update a resource guide that provides information&nbsp;about electric vehicles and their&nbsp;charging infrastructure.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
